ets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 我認同呢想法<br />\n呢幾集真係講多創作呢個領域既野"},{"pid":"247662bfd9689f1c18190c39e2a27dd288f94afd","tid":366014,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文戲都好有水準 呢兩集"},{"pid":"2068103d3d5f2bbb32bbda4c834dec32a3530fc0","tid":366014,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T12:58:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文戲都好有水準 呢兩集</blockquote><br />\n所以talk根本唔係問題，係之前talk得唔好睇"},{"pid":"9e574686c9b937d12c3a3b86ced87082371c6b3b","tid":366014,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文戲都好有水準 呢兩集</blockquote><br />\n所以talk根本唔係問題，係之前talk得唔好睇</blockquote><br />\n近兩集的確係好睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcefc2151d2b01243b532686b93702b54a249d57","tid":366014,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n文戲都好有水準 呢兩集</blockquote><br />\n所以talk根本唔係問題，係之前talk得唔好睇</blockquote><br />\n近兩集的確係好睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good